      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"TreasureShading-ShadingTreasure\">Shading Treasure</h3><p>The gold treasure material is a very simple shader. </p><p>A Voronoi procedural driving reflective roughness attributes drive its textural detail. </p><p>The pattern setup uses a large-scale Voronoi noise, connected to the roughness gain component; this provides a rich textural quality that adds a dirty, ancient feel to the treasure.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"gold_material_B_v01.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391677/gold_material_B_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590492911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=397\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391677/gold_material_B_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590492911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"889\" data-width=\"1700\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657227969\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"gold_material_B_v01.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391677\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"d4832ec9-5112-4f6c-9be4-0ccde0608b09\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391677/gold_material_B_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590492911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=794 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391677/gold_material_B_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590492911&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=397 1x\"></span><hr/>"
